      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "] Under what form these mysterious beings were represented in the Temple is not known. It has been said that the winged bull of the Assyrian sculptures was sometimes called ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
