        "class": "ital",
        "text": "cherub",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " is perhaps a word borrowed from the Assyrian, and the cherubs in the Temple may have had the form of winged bulls. But nothing is certainly known on this subject.",
